^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|Bid 2H. If opener opens 1S and you have 5 cards in hearts, bid 2H. Note that the auction 1S-2H promises 5 hearts. Hopefully, after you read the rest of this section, you will see why. |mb|2h|
