fp||ht|f|cp|8|AT|^B@2^Y@3^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|Your choice of first response is usually identical to what you would do with a medium hand. However, the auction is less complicated from your perspective, because you know your side has game. You can keep making forcing bids (e.g., another new suit) until you determine what the best strain is.|
